{"id": 56403, "date": "2025-04-08T04:00:53", "date_gmt": "2025-04-08T11:00:53", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=56403"}, "modified": "2025-03-28T19:11:38", "modified_gmt": "2025-03-29T02:11:38", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-april-8-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/04/08/kingdom-of-days-april-8-2/", "title": {"rendered": "Kingdom of Days: April 8"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><em><strong>New for 2025:\u00a0</strong>Video for 2014</em></p>\n<p><strong>1976:\u00a0</strong>The second of two nights in Cleveland on the Chicken Scratch Tour features the last &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2020/10/08/cover-me-when-you-walk-in-the-room/\">When You Walk in the Room</a>&#8221; for 33 years.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen - 1976-04-08 Allen Theatre, Cleveland, OH\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/rij7NJhcmoI?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>Bruce sits in with Cats on a Smooth Surface at The Stone Pony in Asbury Park for four songs: &#8220;Proud Mary,&#8221; &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2022/03/18/cover-me-dirty-water/\">Dirty Water,</a>&#8221; &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2020/02/17/cover-me-im-bad-im-nationwide/\">I&#8217;m Bad, I&#8217;m Nationwide</a>,&#8221; and &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2018/11/29/cover-me-lucille/\">Lucille</a>.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen and Cats on a Smooth Surface - Stone Pony  - 1984-04-08\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/E0nGuxZTSNo?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"17337\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-04-08/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/1984-04-08.jpg?fit=389%2C296&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"389,296\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-04-08\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/1984-04-08.jpg?fit=300%2C228&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/1984-04-08.jpg?fit=389%2C296&amp;ssl=1\" class=\" wp-image-17337 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/1984-04-08-300x228.jpg?resize=758%2C576\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"576\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/1984-04-08.jpg?resize=300%2C228&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/1984-04-08.jpg?w=389&amp;ssl=1 389w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1993:\u00a0</strong>At the second of two shows in Zurich, Bruce plays &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2021/12/25/roll-of-the-dice-dancing-in-the-dark/\">Dancing in the Dark</a>&#8221; for the first and only time this year and tour debuts &#8220;Rockin&#8217; All Over the World.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-D126GX2S-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/D126GX2S?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div id=\"v-tvOHIouc-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/tvOHIouc?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Sample Bruce Springsteen Z\u00fcrich 1993 04 08 complete show\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/I-FAIxCEA98?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><strong>1999</strong>: Bruce and the reunited E Street Band play their final rehearsal in Barcelona before the kick-off of the Reunion Tour the following day.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"26396\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1999-04-08/\" da